FBIS4-18171 "drweu062_p_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-062 Daily Report 30 Mar 1994 GREECE Swiss Minister Praises Greek Handling of EU Swiss Minister Praises Greek Handling of EU NC3003184294 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1700 GMT 30 Mar 94 NC3003184294 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] Swiss Foreign Minister Flavio Cotti met his Greek counterpart, Karolos Papoulias, and discussed the situation in the former Yugoslavia, The Former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia [FYROM], Cyprus, and bilateral relations. Cotti, who is officially visiting Greece as the head of a diplomatic delegation, met Alternate Foreign Minister Theodhoros Pangalos this morning. The Swiss foreign minister described the Greek Presidency's preparation for the accession of the four countries to the European Union [EU] as excellent and outstanding. He said he hopes negotiations for his country's accession to the great European family will begin while Greece is holds the presidency.
